sentences: Robbie Merrill (born June 13, 1963) is an American bassist, best known as a founding member of Godsmack and Another Animal.
Good Times, Bad Times... Ten Years of Godsmack
On the back cover of the April 2010 Bass Player magazine issue, Robbie is now an official Gallien-Krueger user.
